Trinity::

She stopped jumping around and watched as Koj walked off.  She sat on 
her hind legs as he disappeared down the hall.  She lowered her head 
down and sighed. She said in a soft, almost depressed voice,"I guess 
I'll have to wait to see mom and dad then huh?"  She lowered her head 
onto her front paws and sighed. She wanted to see her parents again 
so much, but now, all she could do was wait.  She hated waiting.  She 
meowed softly, wishing her parents were with her.
